---
const services = [
  {
    title: "Terapia para Adultos",
    description: "Um espaço para lidar com ansiedade, depressão, estresse e questões de relacionamento.",
    icon: "flower"
  },
  {
    title: "Terapia para Adolescentes",
    description: "Apoio no desenvolvimento da identidade, autoestima e desafios escolares.",
    icon: "sun"
  }
];
---

<section class="py-20 bg-primary-bg relative">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    
    <!-- Spacer for the overlapping profile image on desktop -->
    <div class="h-16 md:h-24 mb-12 block md:hidden"></div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 items-stretch">
      
      <!-- Card 1: Bio Highlight (Text) -->
      <div class="md:col-span-1 bg-card-bg p-8 rounded-2xl flex flex-col justify-center relative overflow-hidden group">
        <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 -mt-4 -mr-4 w-24 h-24 bg-white/20 rounded-full blur-xl group-hover:scale-150 transition-transform duration-700"></div>
        
        <h3 class="font-heading text-2xl font-bold text-text-main mb-4 relative z-10">
          Olá, sou a Elisa
        </h3>
        <p class="text-text-main/90 leading-relaxed mb-6 relative z-10">
          Com mais de 10 anos de experiência clínica, dedico minha vida a ajudar pessoas a transformarem suas dores em força. Acredito que cada história merece ser ouvida com empatia e sem julgamentos.
        </p>
        <a href="/sobre" class="text-accent font-bold uppercase text-sm tracking-wider hover:underline relative z-10 inline-flex items-center gap-2">
          Minha Trajetória
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3" />
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 2: Adultos -->
      <div class="md:col-span-1 bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl border border-stone-100 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow flex flex-col items-center text-center">
        <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-blue-50 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-6 text-accent">
           <!-- Flower Icon -->
           <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-10 w-10" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M12 6.253v13m0-13C10.832 5.477 9.246 5 7.5 5S4.168 5.477 3 6.253v13C4.168 18.477 5.754 18 7.5 18s3.332.477 4.5 1.253m0-13C13.168 5.477 14.754 5 16.5 5c1.747 0 3.332.477 4.5 1.253v13C19.832 18.477 18.247 18 16.5 18c-1.746 0-3.332.477-4.5 1.253" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-heading text-xl font-bold text-text-main mb-3">Terapia para Adultos</h3>
        <p class="text-text-main/70">
            Um espaço seguro para lidar com ansiedade, depressão e reescrever sua história pessoal.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 3: Adolescentes -->
      <div class="md:col-span-1 bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl border border-stone-100 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow flex flex-col items-center text-center">
        <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-orange-50 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-6 text-orange-400">
            <!-- Sun Icon -->
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-10 w-10" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M12 3v1m0 16v1m9-9h-1M4 12H3m15.364 6.364l-.707-.707M6.343 6.343l-.707-.707m12.728 0l-.707.707M6.343 17.657l-.707.707M16 12a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0z" />
            </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-heading text-xl font-bold text-text-main mb-3">Terapia para Adolescentes</h3>
        <p class="text-text-main/70">
            Apoio no desenvolvimento da identidade, fortalecimento da autoestima e desafios escolares.
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
